{
  "page": "Menagerie",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>menagerie</b> is a private collection of captive <a href=\"/index.php/Bestiary\" title=\"Bestiary\">animals</a>, frequently exotic, kept for display.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Known_menageries\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known menageries</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Braavos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Braavos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Lannisport\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lannisport</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Pentos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Pentos</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_menageries\">Known menageries</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known menageries\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Braavos\">Braavos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Braavos\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord%27s_menagerie\" title=\"Sealord&#39;s menagerie\">Sealord's menagerie</a>, located in the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord%27s_Palace\" title=\"Sealord&#39;s Palace\">Sealord's Palace</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>, is renowned throughout the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf827-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Braavosi <a href=\"/index.php/Ship\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ship\">ship</a> captains bring queer animals from around the world to the Sealord's menagerie.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Lannisport\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>'s menagerie used to include a grey <a href=\"/index.php/Elephant\" title=\"Elephant\">elephant</a>, but the animal died when <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> was seven years old (either <a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a>).<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pentos\">Pentos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Pentos\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Magister\" title=\"Magister\">Magister</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> has a menagerie in his <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">manse</a> that includes a <a href=\"/index.php/Panther\" title=\"Panther\">panther</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The menagerie of the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a> includes a pride of <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lions</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_scenes\">Behind the scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Real-world <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Menagerie\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Menagerie\">menageries</a> are considered to be the ancestors of modern <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zoo\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Zoo\">zoos</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Menagerie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf827-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf827_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; The Free Cities&#32;(Braavos).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_50\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 50\">Chapter 50</a>, Arya IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, Tyrion I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406132442\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.053 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 504/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8787/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1873/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 106/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2240/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   44.923      1 -total\n 69.01%   30.999      2 Template:Date\n 24.74%   11.114      5 Template:Ref\n 15.15%    6.804      5 Template:Ref/core\n  5.02%    2.253      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:32348-0!canonical and timestamp 20260406132451 and revision id 335640\n -->\n",
